install nodejs from nodejs.org website 

open cmd and type the below cmds 

npm install -g angular

npm install -g typescript

npm install -g @angular/cli

ng version

*Create folder and redirect to the folder in the terminal*


ng new angulardemo1

install visual studio code open visual studio code ->file->open folder->select the  angular project folder which was created before by the cmd 


Terminal->change default terminal to cmd(powershell->select command prompt) (click on the downdown arrow in terminal select default profile and select cmd in it)
Terminal->new terminal.

ng serve -o 
